%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 85baba632ea3086499e53d211ed4c41a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day1 - Lola Mom Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - speaker: 3
    text: Welcome to Cash Me If You Can!
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 0
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 1
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: "I am Lola mom, and I am here to guide you through the Cash Me If You Can
      app\r!\n"
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 0
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 1
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: This is where you log down your expenses. To start, go ahead and click
      the 'Log Expenses'.
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 1
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 1
    lolaStep: 2
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: Over here is your Savings Meter. Here you get to see and track how far
      or near you are from your savings goal!
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 2
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 3
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: Track each day. Consistency is key!
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 3
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 3
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: 'Moving on to your expenses, Shown here is your chosen Budget Method: [METHOD]'
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 4
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 3
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: 'Now, this is your expense tab:'
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 5
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 3
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: Both your needs and wants are in one tab.
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 5
    dependsOnBudget: 1
    requiredBudget: 1
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 3
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: "Now be careful! Just because you can spend more on wants doesn\u2019t
      mean you should! "
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 5
    dependsOnBudget: 1
    requiredBudget: 1
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 3
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: 'Here, your Needs and Wants are separated into 2 tabs, less confusion but
      still try not to over spend! '
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 5
    dependsOnBudget: 1
    requiredBudget: 2
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 3
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: Down here, are your choices of items to spend on.
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 6
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 3
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: Now, decide, tap to select for your Needs!
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 6
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 1
    lolaStep: 4
    requiresValidAllocation: 1
  - speaker: 3
    text: Great! Next, is your Wants, go ahead and click the wants button
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 5
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 1
    lolaStep: 5
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: Again, decide, tap to select for your Wants!
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 6
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 1
    lolaStep: 6
    requiresValidAllocation: 1
  - speaker: 3
    text: Great! Now, hit confirm and move on with your day iha!
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 7
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 1
    lolaStep: 7
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: One last thing, You can track your expenses here and see where your money
      goes. Go ahead and click the 'Expense Tracker' button
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 8
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 1
    lolaStep: 8
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: Only one person to blame when you don't know where it went!
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 0
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 10
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: "Watch out for Alex\u2019s Happiness Meter so stress doesn't take over
      Alex\u2019s decision making, make sure it doesn't drop below 30%!"
    useSpotlight: 1
    spotlightIndex: 0
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 10
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: Go ahead and click the back button for now.
    useSpotlight: 0
    spotlightIndex: 0
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 1
    lolaStep: 10
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - speaker: 3
    text: And that's about it. Goodluck budgeting your expenses!
    useSpotlight: 0
    spotlightIndex: 0
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 11
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
